-Shit.
-(shouts indistinctly)

22:29.909 --> 22:31.343
Shit!

22:36.615 --> 22:38.717
You're gonna need
some antibiotics.

22:38.750 --> 22:40.352
It's gonna get infected.

22:43.455 --> 22:45.590
What's wrong?

22:45.624 --> 22:49.594
Nada. Thinking about my gym,
not a wrestling gym, no más.

22:49.628 --> 22:51.831
My boxing gym, too.

22:51.864 --> 22:54.433
And in two months,
como dijiste.

22:56.368 --> 22:58.838
Where's Pedro?
I'll paint the floor red.

22:58.871 --> 23:01.340
It'll be purita quality.

23:01.373 --> 23:04.243
All-steel frame,
corner cushions,

23:04.276 --> 23:07.012
ring padding, ring skirts.

23:07.046 --> 23:08.780
(chuckles)

23:08.814 --> 23:11.250
(speaks Spanish)

23:11.283 --> 23:14.019
(chuckles)

23:14.053 --> 23:15.888
(gunshot)

23:17.389 --> 23:19.191
(gunshots)

23:19.224 --> 23:22.094
(door creaking)
Pedro!

23:22.127 --> 23:24.363
Pedro, what did you do?

23:24.396 --> 23:27.099
I shot a rat.

23:27.132 --> 23:28.533
Why?

23:28.567 --> 23:30.035
It was coming at me.

23:30.069 --> 23:32.371
GUSTAVO: That's not a rat.

23:32.404 --> 23:34.373
Fuck you, it's not a rat.
Look at it.

23:34.406 --> 23:35.807
This is un possum, pendejo.

23:35.841 --> 23:37.376
Possums are nocturnal.

23:37.409 --> 23:39.311
Who gives a shit what it is?

23:39.344 --> 23:42.714
We have a house full of coke
and a body in your trunk.

23:42.747 --> 23:44.316
What if somebody calls the cops?

23:44.349 --> 23:46.051
You got his blood on you.

23:46.085 --> 23:48.387
Go change.
(sniffs)

23:48.420 --> 23:50.722
Why?

23:50.755 --> 23:53.425
Just gonna get
all dirty again.

23:55.094 --> 23:57.062
Oso.

23:57.096 --> 23:59.731
Can you --
can you put it in the trunk?

23:59.764 --> 24:01.700
We'll bury it with Enrique.

24:11.610 --> 24:13.445
You have a bag?

24:14.880 --> 24:16.581
♪ ...to me
(pounding on trunk)

24:16.615 --> 24:18.250
-KARVEL: Let me up outta here!
-Shit.

24:18.283 --> 24:20.920
Yeah, yeah. Crank it, crank it.
(volume increases)

24:20.953 --> 24:23.923
AIR SUPPLY: ♪ I used to think
I was tied to a heartache ♪

24:23.956 --> 24:27.927
♪ That was the heartbreak,
but now that I've found you ♪

24:27.960 --> 24:32.031
♪ Even the nights are better
♪ Even the nights are better

24:32.064 --> 24:35.767
♪ Now that we're here together ♪
Now that we're here together ♪

24:35.800 --> 24:39.271
♪ Even the nights are better
♪ Even the nights are better

24:39.304 --> 24:44.876
(Karvel shouting indistinctly) ♪
Since I found you, oh, whoa, whoa ♪

24:44.910 --> 24:48.447
♪ Even the days are brighter

24:48.480 --> 24:50.449
♪ When someone you love's...
(muffled thud)

24:50.482 --> 24:56.521
♪♪

24:56.555 --> 24:59.224
♪ Turn off
that washing machine ♪

24:59.258 --> 25:00.859
Hey, listen.

25:00.892 --> 25:02.794
(volume decreases)

25:02.827 --> 25:04.896
♪♪

25:04.930 --> 25:06.465
Did he pass out?

25:06.498 --> 25:09.634
♪ Call up
all your girlfriends ♪

25:09.668 --> 25:12.137
(thudding)

25:12.171 --> 25:15.140
Oh, shit! Oh, shit!
He's got a crowbar!

25:15.174 --> 25:16.641
Give me the gun! Give me
the gun! Give me the gun!

25:16.675 --> 25:18.577
Hurry up! Give me that shit!
(gunshot)

25:18.610 --> 25:20.245
Ow!
Fuck!

25:20.279 --> 25:22.481
(gunshots)

25:22.514 --> 25:24.749
Did you get him?

25:24.783 --> 25:26.085
Shit!
(screams)

25:26.118 --> 25:29.721
(all shouting indistinctly)

25:29.754 --> 25:32.224
I'm fucking driving, man! Shit!
(tires screeching)

25:32.257 --> 25:34.293
(shouting indistinctly)

25:38.197 --> 25:41.366
♪♪

25:47.039 --> 25:48.240
Shoot!
(gunshots)

25:48.273 --> 25:50.109
Aah!

25:50.142 --> 25:51.910
(thud)
(screaming)

25:51.943 --> 25:54.246
Shit.

25:54.279 --> 25:56.648
I ain't jumpin' down that.

26:01.720 --> 26:04.723
(birds chirping)

26:13.232 --> 26:15.734
ALEJANDRO: Coke's ready.
Help me load the Jeep.

26:18.570 --> 26:20.872
Hey.

26:20.905 --> 26:23.142
We need a better way.

26:26.245 --> 26:28.313
What?

26:28.347 --> 26:31.116
Transporting the coca leaves
from Colombia or Peru

26:31.150 --> 26:32.551
or wherever the fuck.

26:32.584 --> 26:34.319
Processing it here
doesn't make any sense.

26:34.353 --> 26:36.221
We should be synthesizing it
where it's grown

26:36.255 --> 26:37.789
and transporting it after.

26:37.822 --> 26:41.060
Means dealing with Colombians.
Trying to avoid that.

26:41.093 --> 26:43.462
What's that?

26:43.495 --> 26:45.864
Oh, just give me a minute,
will you?

26:54.173 --> 26:57.176
♪♪

27:29.541 --> 27:33.145
(man shouting in Spanish)

27:34.479 --> 27:36.115
(Popeye crying)

27:36.148 --> 27:37.849
(man continues shouting
in Spanish)

27:37.882 --> 27:39.951
I saw the kid come out of
this tree when I first arrived.

27:39.984 --> 27:42.387
I climbed up there later,
and I found this.

27:42.421 --> 27:44.556
(shouting in Spanish continues)

27:44.589 --> 27:47.359
It's called a firefly,
an infrared transmitter.

27:47.392 --> 27:50.529
Anybody with a receiver
can locate it.

27:50.562 --> 27:53.532
And thus the camp.

27:53.565 --> 27:57.035
Someone in a helicopter, say.

27:57.068 --> 27:58.970
The only reason
they haven't attacked yet

27:59.003 --> 28:00.805
is he didn't attach
the battery properly.

28:00.839 --> 28:03.308
I can't believe
I didn't see this.

28:03.342 --> 28:07.045
Sandinistas are smart,
using a kid. But...

28:07.078 --> 28:08.380
-(man shouts in Spanish)
-POPEYE: No, no, no.

28:08.413 --> 28:10.982
He asked a lot of questions.

28:11.015 --> 28:14.553
And he knew about the CIA.
And he was from Bocay.

28:14.586 --> 28:16.321
(man and Popeye
shouting in Spanish)

28:16.355 --> 28:19.958
But, uh, mostly I can tell
when someone's lying to me.

28:21.693 --> 28:23.562
Give it to me.

28:23.595 --> 28:25.797
(shouting in Spanish continues)

28:30.435 --> 28:33.338
We put it in a tree
5 miles east.

28:33.372 --> 28:35.374
When the helicopters come,
we'll shoot them down.

28:42.381 --> 28:44.849
He could be useful. You could
turn him into a double.

28:44.883 --> 28:47.786
Can't risk it.
He's just a kid.

28:47.819 --> 28:51.055
A kid who tried
to kill us all.

29:02.967 --> 29:05.870
(exhales deeply)

29:05.904 --> 29:09.874
(inhales sharply)

29:09.908 --> 29:11.910
(Lucia speaks Spanish)

29:38.102 --> 29:40.272
You've seen people die
before.

29:44.609 --> 29:46.511
Max.

29:46.545 --> 29:50.349
Enrique.

29:50.382 --> 29:52.551
One other.

29:55.520 --> 29:56.821
¿Y tú?

29:56.855 --> 30:00.925
You've seen someone
die before?

30:00.959 --> 30:03.328
Hmm?

30:03.362 --> 30:04.796
Nunca.

30:09.734 --> 30:12.737
(pager beeping and vibrating)

30:15.139 --> 30:17.776
(sniffles)
(beeping continues)

30:17.809 --> 30:19.778
Fuck! Fuck!

30:19.811 --> 30:22.314
9-1-1. My dad. I gotta go.

30:24.316 --> 30:27.118
(sniffles) Give me your keys.
I can't take my car.

30:27.151 --> 30:29.120
There's all this shit
in the trunk. Come on.

30:29.153 --> 30:32.291
You're not right, ese.
Ramiro pages him, he has to go.

30:32.324 --> 30:35.394
He's suspicious if he doesn't. Yeah.
Hand over your keys, you fucking oaf.

30:50.742 --> 30:52.744
(speaks Spanish)

30:54.112 --> 30:57.316
I know what happened.

30:57.349 --> 31:00.452
The fuck you talkin' about?
In Enrique's kitchen.

31:02.421 --> 31:05.990
When Gustavo was knocked out,

31:06.024 --> 31:09.260
and that fucking animal
was on top of me,

31:09.294 --> 31:14.198
with his hands around my neck,
choking me to death.

31:16.100 --> 31:18.670
And you just stood there

31:18.703 --> 31:22.073
with that fucking knife,
staring.

31:22.106 --> 31:24.709
You don't know what you're saying.
You froze!

31:27.312 --> 31:32.517
If Gustavo hadn't woken up,
Pedro, I'd be dead.

31:32.551 --> 31:35.720
You know it, and I know it.

31:39.223 --> 31:41.025
Before you go to your father's,
you have to go home

31:41.059 --> 31:42.694
and put on
your own clothes first.

31:42.727 --> 31:46.698
And once you're there,
keep your head up.

31:46.731 --> 31:49.100
Just like that.
And look him in the eye.

31:49.133 --> 31:50.535
(sniffs)

31:50.569 --> 31:52.871
Speak normally.

31:52.904 --> 31:55.940
Be calm.

31:55.974 --> 31:57.409
Say it.

31:58.977 --> 32:03.382
I have to go home first,
put on my own clothes,

32:03.415 --> 32:07.619
keep my head up,
look him in the eye.

32:07.652 --> 32:09.354
Be normal.

32:12.156 --> 32:15.627
You fuck this up,
and I'm gonna kill you.

32:15.660 --> 32:17.095
(laughs)

32:19.163 --> 32:21.900
Gustavo!

32:21.933 --> 32:24.369
(sighs, sniffs)

32:26.871 --> 32:29.273
(beads clacking)

32:30.609 --> 32:34.413
(keys jangling)

32:34.446 --> 32:36.080
(laughs)

32:36.114 --> 32:38.617
Come back after it's done.

32:53.565 --> 32:56.435
How the hell this motherfucker
still alive?

32:56.468 --> 32:59.604
I don't know.
Maybe he zombified.

32:59.638 --> 33:01.105
You stupid. You stupid.

33:01.139 --> 33:03.542
Yeah, you know he like
an animal.

33:05.243 --> 33:07.612
Can't see no more blood.

33:07.646 --> 33:10.281
Where'd it go?
Nigga, I don't know.

33:10.314 --> 33:12.451
What am I, a fucking Navajo?

33:12.484 --> 33:14.553
Shit!

33:19.491 --> 33:21.626
Hey, Saint.

33:21.660 --> 33:23.995
Found a trail.

33:27.832 --> 33:30.835
(breathing heavily)

33:32.837 --> 33:35.106
(coughs)

33:44.916 --> 33:48.286
(crows cawing)

33:57.529 --> 33:59.430
(sniffles)

34:13.111 --> 34:15.446
Please...

34:31.730 --> 34:33.331
(gunshot)

34:38.503 --> 34:40.038
(gunshot)

34:40.071 --> 34:43.742
(gunshot echoing)

35:02.594 --> 35:04.162
Lucia...

35:04.195 --> 35:07.298
(speaking Spanish)

35:07.331 --> 35:10.301
(woman screaming,
man shouting in Spanish)

35:10.334 --> 35:15.807
(woman continues screaming)

35:15.840 --> 35:17.175
(footsteps approach)

35:17.208 --> 35:18.843
(door creaking)

35:23.514 --> 35:25.850
(gunshot)
(body thuds)

35:25.884 --> 35:27.819
(woman screaming)

35:27.852 --> 35:30.855
(footsteps approaching)

35:32.691 --> 35:34.125
(blows air)

35:35.393 --> 35:37.061
You should sleep.

35:38.730 --> 35:40.732
You telling me what to do?

35:42.801 --> 35:44.335
No.

35:44.368 --> 35:46.037
'Cause, you know...

35:49.140 --> 35:51.309
Technically, I'm your boss.

35:54.713 --> 35:56.480
Sorry, patrona.
(chuckles)

35:58.249 --> 35:59.951
I'm just kidding.

35:59.984 --> 36:03.121
(sighs)

36:03.154 --> 36:06.524
I just saw you...

36:06.557 --> 36:08.893
crush a man's skull

36:08.927 --> 36:11.395
with your bare hands.

36:11.429 --> 36:14.633
I think that boss/employee
relationship

36:14.666 --> 36:17.068
flew out the window.

36:21.505 --> 36:23.341
What's going on with that?

36:24.843 --> 36:27.011
I don't know.

36:30.348 --> 36:32.250
(blows air)

36:37.188 --> 36:39.858
Do you have any brothers
or sisters?

36:42.360 --> 36:43.862
No.

37:07.819 --> 37:09.553
(door opens)

37:11.723 --> 37:13.357
How did it go?

37:13.391 --> 37:14.826
(keys jangle)

37:19.898 --> 37:22.366
Arturo went
to Enrique's house,

37:22.400 --> 37:24.035
three hours after we'd left.

37:24.068 --> 37:26.204
Fuck.

37:26.237 --> 37:28.139
(chuckles)

37:28.172 --> 37:30.374
That was close.
We could've still been there.

37:30.408 --> 37:32.476
Yeah, but it worked.

37:32.510 --> 37:36.547
Ramiro thinks Enrique ran off
after stealing the money.

37:36.580 --> 37:38.549
Good.

37:38.582 --> 37:42.353
Come on. It's time.
Let's go.

37:51.029 --> 37:53.497
(keys jangle, door opens)

37:53.531 --> 37:56.701
(indistinct conversation
in Spanish)

38:01.940 --> 38:04.275
I heard you wanted
to let the kid go.

38:08.046 --> 38:10.614
Do you know how much damage
that would've done?

38:11.783 --> 38:16.320
We're not
flying into Hawthorne.

38:16.354 --> 38:19.023
(sighs) What?

38:19.057 --> 38:21.525
Didn't have time to vet
the customs guys.

38:23.962 --> 38:25.329
Where we gonna land, then?

38:25.363 --> 38:26.798
(gunshot in distance)

38:44.248 --> 38:46.050
I'll come back in 10
to pick you up.

38:46.084 --> 38:47.651
(engine starts)

38:51.222 --> 38:52.656
(Jeep departs)

38:57.428 --> 39:00.398
♪♪

39:09.507 --> 39:11.009
(monkey chitters)

39:16.247 --> 39:19.117
(lowered voice) Go.
Get the fuck out of here.

39:24.188 --> 39:28.326
In a few weeks, you should
start receiving shipments.

39:28.359 --> 39:32.864
Supplies and weapons
and whatever you need.

39:40.271 --> 39:43.107
Give this to Alejandro.

39:44.876 --> 39:49.213
Tell him, "Don't forget."

39:57.155 --> 39:58.722
(papers rustling)

40:04.462 --> 40:07.465
(hip-hop music playing)

40:13.304 --> 40:15.206
Y'all had an animal
back there?

40:15.239 --> 40:19.110
Uh, yeah.

40:19.143 --> 40:20.811
I'll give you $23K.

40:20.845 --> 40:22.646
Twenty-th-- I bought it
yesterday. It's brand-new.

40:22.680 --> 40:25.383
And the custom rims.

40:25.416 --> 40:27.451
Maybe.

40:27.485 --> 40:32.123
But you sure can fuck up
an upholstery job in 24 hours.

40:32.156 --> 40:33.724
♪♪

40:33.757 --> 40:35.994
All right, man. One sec.

40:36.027 --> 40:38.562
Let me confer with
my business associate.

40:38.596 --> 40:42.566
♪♪

40:42.600 --> 40:44.402
You the one went
to that fancy school,

40:44.435 --> 40:48.172
but my math tell me, that ain't
enough to pay that Israeli.

40:48.206 --> 40:49.740
Mm.

40:49.773 --> 40:52.743
♪♪

40:52.776 --> 40:55.113
I got something else
I could sell.

41:00.351 --> 41:03.421
MAN:
You are full of surprises.

41:03.454 --> 41:06.590
Scraggly-ass kid

41:06.624 --> 41:08.759
with a Caddy
and a crotch rocket.

41:08.792 --> 41:12.430
Hey, can I have this?

41:12.463 --> 41:14.832
A'ight.

41:14.865 --> 41:17.368
I'll take it.

41:17.401 --> 41:19.537
I'll give you $800.

41:19.570 --> 41:21.705
♪♪

41:21.739 --> 41:27.278
A kid like you gonna do
with all that money anyway?

41:27.311 --> 41:29.914
(dog barking in distance)
LEON: Now we re-up.

41:32.216 --> 41:33.617
(siren wailing in distance)

41:33.651 --> 41:36.454
Listen, uh, thanks
for me, you know...

41:36.487 --> 41:38.322
Hey, don't worry 'bout it.

41:46.897 --> 41:49.200
Hey, where you goin'?

41:49.233 --> 41:50.634
Saint!

41:50.668 --> 41:52.470
Hit me tomorrow.

41:52.503 --> 41:55.073
(helicopter blades whirring)

41:55.106 --> 41:58.076
(dog barking in distance)

41:58.109 --> 42:01.779
♪♪

42:11.122 --> 42:12.656
You should invest in
your own shovel

42:12.690 --> 42:15.926
if you're in it
for the long haul.

42:15.960 --> 42:20.831
And always keep plenty
of heavy duty garbage bags

42:20.864 --> 42:22.666
in the trunk of your car.

42:22.700 --> 42:25.936
♪♪

42:25.970 --> 42:27.438
And rubber gloves.

42:29.540 --> 42:32.843
Rubbing alcohol.

42:32.876 --> 42:34.845
Air freshener.

42:34.878 --> 42:36.247
Yo, Muir.

42:36.280 --> 42:38.616
Huh?

42:38.649 --> 42:41.352
♪♪

42:41.385 --> 42:42.920
Set the kid up
with 3 more kilos.

42:42.953 --> 42:46.857
Uh, actually, I'm...
I'm good.

42:46.890 --> 42:50.861
♪♪

42:50.894 --> 42:53.464
What?

42:53.497 --> 42:55.066
I'm out.

42:56.967 --> 42:58.202
♪♪

42:58.236 --> 43:00.871
Thank you.

43:00.904 --> 43:03.941
(chuckles)

43:03.974 --> 43:07.045
Well...

43:07.078 --> 43:10.148
You lasted longer than
I thought you would, kid.

43:10.181 --> 43:11.549
(clicks tongue)

43:11.582 --> 43:13.584
This isn't for everybody.

43:15.686 --> 43:17.888
Hey, girl.

43:17.921 --> 43:19.323
Why don't you get out
of the pool

43:19.357 --> 43:22.393
and bring your tight ass
over here?

43:22.426 --> 43:25.229
(Avi laughs)

43:25.263 --> 43:27.565
♪♪

43:27.598 --> 43:31.102
♪ Mmm, mmm, mmm

43:40.878 --> 43:45.083
♪ Mmm, mmm, mmm

43:45.116 --> 43:47.285
♪♪

45:21.945 --> 45:24.815
-- Captions by VITA --
